Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be taking my leave of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you've been assigned to. It's called the Time-Keeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find a way there by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata will be assigned to the 1221st Platoon in Seize, Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Republic of Helvetia Army Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1320, mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize, the city of springs and glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to report in at 1500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to play music with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Route check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D flat... what a wonderful note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,¥10.25...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... What a beautiful doll-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten got lost amid all the hustle and bustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, kittens just love wandering around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would agree if it had been a wild cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this one was a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really startled me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something fabulous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she from the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll have a good fortune for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you get me wet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're frickin' soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch i-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ... Come on, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's a pretty easy target...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you not even try to dodge them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This type of fabric is very easy to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it originated from a legend we have here in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of flame protecting the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the imposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maintenence is complete, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That busybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late! She's late! She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way here to welcome her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just calm down and wait patiently, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your dad give this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me use your bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... kind of have a tendency to get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I met awesome people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get lost, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recognize notes easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's somehow comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn... is that thing worth more than your life!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to leave. I have something to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell must've been really precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long before the world became like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a winged demon lived in the ravines of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It showered fire down upon the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing great suffering to the people who lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It kidnapped the maidens who lived here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens did not despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called upon one another using the golden horn bestowed upon them by the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thus escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They defeated the demon and took its head
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by borrowing the power of a great spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the head would not cease spewing its flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had continued to do so, then the entire city would have been engulfed by fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to halt the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the maidens took turns embracing the demon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the city poured water upon the maidens every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a year, the fire was finally extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've held the water festival in order to appease the souls of the maidens who saved the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the recruit's not coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, look at Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How very fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we made the right decision in letting her handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we draw lots...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretty much suck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have fun when I get lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but only because I meet people I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep believing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your sound will resound without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shall resound without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiden of flame, rest here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace the demon and appease the curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it will never again awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the demon arisen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let my sound reach someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will resound and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake your ass up, Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long were you planning to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Keeping Fortress, the garrison of the 1221st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize for what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm just giving you a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so reckless in the future, though, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is just an ordinary bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to play trumpet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why this fortress is known as the Time-Keeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be your trumpet instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working with you, Sergeant Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Felicia- the captain wants us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't address each other with military ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Ms. Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go ahead and get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear a wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever's playing now is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:47.20,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's get friendship, love, and other feelings together,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:50.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and play out how important they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I cried from joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.50,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I laughed from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:20.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}But that's all a part of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:23.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and tells me that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:27.92,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's take this slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:29.50,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.01,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you tell me how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.11,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:40.85,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Even when friendship and love waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:41.13,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I know, you know, will be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:46.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I hope this melody will ring forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:47.02,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you count my precious flower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:52.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Overflowing words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:58.83,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:03.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you hear our harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.74,0:24:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: First Campaign - The Story of the Chair.
